parts.text:
<OUTPUT_JSON>[
  {
    "selector": "select[name*=report i]",
    "action": "select_option",
    "value": "{{report_type}}",
    "description": "Select the desired report type from the dropdown. The value for '{{report_type}}' (e.g., 'Sales Summary Q3', 'Financial Performance YTD') needs to be provided at runtime."
  },
  {
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"generate\" i)",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Click the 'Generate' button to produce the selected report on the screen or in the background."
  },
  {
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"export\" i)",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Click the 'Export' button to prepare the generated report for download, possibly choosing a format (e.g., PDF, CSV, XLSX)."
  },
  {
    "selector": "a:has-text(\"download\" i)",
    "action": "click",
    "description": "Click the 'Download' link to save the exported report file to the local system."
  }
]</OUTPUT_JSON>
